        <!-- Section 16: Real-World Timeline -->
        <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-indigo-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-indigo-400 pl-4">Real-World Project Timeline</h2>

        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">Here's what a typical chatbot project looks like week by week. This assumes a RAG chatbot with one integration (e.g., booking):</p>

        <div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-indigo-500/30 bg-indigo-950/10">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="shrink-0 w-16 text-xs font-mono text-indigo-400">Week 1</div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm text-white font-medium">Discovery & Architecture</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Stakeholder interviews, content audit, decide model + platform, write project spec</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="shrink-0 w-16 text-xs font-mono text-indigo-400">Week 2</div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm text-white font-medium">Knowledge Base</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Collect content, clean and chunk, build embedding pipeline, populate vector DB</p>
              </div>
            </div>
